[0.029, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[40;1H\u001b[38;5;172m\u001b[2m> /agent research GOAL: Investigate population genetics of early Americans after Beringian migration, focusing on genetic diversity, founding populations, and demographic patterns. FORMAT: Structured analysis with genetic evidence, population estimates, and timeline. CONSTRAINTS: Focus on peer-reviewed genetic studies, distinguish between mtDNA/Y-chromosome/autosomal evidence, include confidence levels for claims. VERBATIM: Beringia, early American population genetics, founding populations. SUCCESS: Comprehensive overview with specific genetic markers, population bottleneck evidence, and demographic reconstructions with source citations.\u001b[38;5;252m\u001b[0m\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b8"]
